    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small decorative fobs or functional objects attached to a chain or strap that is attached to a watch placed in a pocket. For the chains attached to the fob, use "fob chains."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
